‚ćĚ Insert dummy data into the database for testing
‚ćĚ First tests considered:
‚ćĚ - /videos?search= should return all videos with matching terms
‚ćĚ - /videos?presenter=p_name should return all videos by presenter p_name
‚ćĚ - /videos?search=p_name       should include videos by presenter p_name
‚ćĚ FIXME this is not comprehensive. Fields essential to the video library are used, but many are not.

‚ćĚ Start by generating joined data and deconstructing it into the normalised database, then loop over each table and insert.

